{"id": 2329, "genre": 1000, "title": "如何挑选/逛实体店铺让你更像一个中产阶级？", "description": "人是铁，范儿是钢，一天不装憋得慌。对于中产阶级这个可爱的群体，我们充满了爱意。好奇心研究所会不定期推出紧跟时代节奏的“中产阶级装腔指南”，和大家一起分享研究生活的心得。（题图来自：视觉中国 ©️ Ikon Images）", "record_count": 8613, "comment_count": 55, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180507182012Mucgw0ldskGvEqUJ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-05-08T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4141, "title": "如何挑选/逛实体店铺让你更像一个中产阶级？", "content": "如何挑选/逛实体店铺让你更像一个中产阶级？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 280422, "content": "店面装潢对标双年展，艺术品比商品还显眼的那种", "image": "img/option/option/20180507234125H6Lm8Ot9pi7B0hxj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 280423, "content": "饭馆地面铺花砖，灯光打足，特别适合拍照", "image": "img/option/option/20180507232318C8cV9fY0gXThnb71.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 280424, "content": "洗手间用黄铜装饰，马桶还带加热盖", "image": "img/option/option/20180507184756eVB7LESymWgNnkHo.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 280425, "content": "自带进口超市的商场才是合格的商场", "image": "img/option/option/20180507184547Q9on5tmsrL7UuzN1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 280427, "content": "不管水果摊还是餐厅，有机是个加分项", "image": "img/option/option/20180507184223uHniZKm19DjQe7yl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 280428, "content": "店长是一只猫，柴犬也行，反正不是人类", "image": "img/option/option/20180507183539lFufWpK7Q2ZN0AJe.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 280429, "content": "藏在巷子里、挂着“在地手作美食”牌子的小馆子", "image": "img/option/option/20180507183102Utvgr7swcbPBhMJH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 280430, "content": "博主推过的饮品店，虽然不屑排队但找机会总要尝的", "image": "img/option/option/20180507182625lAQBwdqNfY14zoEn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 280431, "content": "卖跨界联名款的品牌店，比如优衣库 X 少年Jump", "image": "img/option/option/20180507181951PoSzkIWGMvpNjCsx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}